  "label": "Sevrin Latch",
  "description": "This individual presents as an animated corpse of late middle years, with a stiff, economy of motion that defines the Vitrifall Hollow dead. Brown eyes sit deep beneath a heavy brow ridge, fixed in an unblinking stare; the face is drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and a squared jaw. Black hair persists in thin, uneven lengths, and the skinTone is zombie, split by long-set fissures and dried abrasions that no longer heal. The hands are broad and blunt-fingered, bearing ingrained grime and old callus that attest to a lifetime of manual labor now continued without breath.",
